\c 36
\s Inzalo kaEsawu
\p
\v 1 Lezi-ke yizizukulwana zikaEsawu, onguEdoma\x + \xt 25.30.\x*.
\v 2 UEsawu wathatha abafazi bakhe kumadodakazi eKhanani\x + \xt 26.34.\x*, uAda indodakazi kaEloni umHethi, loAholibama indodakazi kaAna\x + \xt 36.14,18,25.\x*, indodakazi kaZibeyoni umHivi,
\v 3 loBasemathi indodakazi kaIshmayeli\x + \xt 28.9.\x* udadewabo kaNebayothi.
\v 4 UAda wasemzalela uEsawu uElifazi; uBasemathi wasezala uRehuweli\x + \xt 36.10. 1 Lan. 1.35.\x*;
\v 5 uAholibama wasezala uJewushi loJalama loKora; la ngamadodana kaEsawu awazalelwa elizweni leKhanani.
\v 6 UEsawu wasethatha omkakhe lamadodana akhe lamadodakazi akhe, layo yonke imiphefumulo yendlu yakhe, lenkomo zakhe lezifuyo zakhe zonke lempahla yakhe yonke ayeyizuzile elizweni leKhanani, wasesiya kwe\add linye\add* ilizwe esuka ebusweni bukaJakobe umfowabo.
\v 7 Ngoba imfuyo yabo yayinkulu okungangokuthi bangehlale ndawonye\x + \xt 13.6.\x*, lelizwe abebehlala kulo njengabemzini, lalingebathwale ngenxa yezifuyo zabo\x + \xt 17.8; 28.4; 37.1.\x*.
\v 8 UEsawu wasehlala entabeni iSeyiri\x + \xt 32.3.\x*; uEsawu nguEdoma\x + \xt 36.1,19.\x*.
\p
\v 9 Lezi-ke yizizukulwana zikaEsawu, uyise wabakoEdoma, entabeni iSeyiri;
\v 10 la ngamabizo amadodana kaEsawu, uElifazi\x + \xt 1 Lan. 1.35.\x* indodana kaAda\x + \xt 36.4.\x* umkaEsawu, uRehuweli indodana kaBasemathi umkaEsawu.
\v 11 Lamadodana kaElifazi ayengoTemani, uOmari, uZefo, loGatama, loKenazi.
\v 12 UTimina-ke wayengumfazi omncane kaElifazi indodana kaEsawu, wamzalela uElifazi uAmaleki\x + \xt Eks. 17.8-16. Nani 24.20. 1 Sam. 15.2,3.\x*; la ngamadodana kaAda umkaEsawu.
\v 13 Lala ngamadodana kaRehuweli, oNahathi loZera, uShama loMiza; la ngamadodana kaBasemathi umkaEsawu.
\p
\v 14 Njalo la ngamadodana kaAholibama\x + \xt 36.2.\x* indodakazi kaAna, indodakazi kaZibeyoni umkaEsawu; wasemzalela uEsawu uJewushi loJalama loKora.
\p
\v 15 Lezi yizinduna zamadodana kaEsawu; amadodana kaElifazi izibulo likaEsawu\x + \xt 36.11,12.\x*: Induna uTemani, induna uOmari, induna uZefo, induna uKenazi,
\v 16 induna uKora, induna uGatama, induna uAmaleki; lezi zinduna zikaElifazi elizweni leEdoma; la ngamadodana kaAda.
\p
\v 17 Futhi la ngamadodana kaRehuweli indodana kaEsawu\x + \xt 36.13.\x*: Induna uNahathi, induna uZera, induna uShama, induna uMiza; lezi zinduna zikaRehuweli elizweni leEdoma; la ngamadodana kaBasemathi umkaEsawu.
\p
\v 18 Njalo la ngamadodana kaAholibama, umkaEsawu\x + \xt 36.14.\x*: Induna uJewushi, induna uJalama, induna uKora; lezi zinduna zikaAholibama, indodakazi kaAna, umkaEsawu.
\v 19 La ngamadodana kaEsawu, futhi lezi zinduna zawo; unguEdoma\x + \xt 36.1,8.\x*.
\s Inzalo kaSeyiri
\p
\v 20 La ngamadodana kaSeyiri\x + \xt 1 Lan. 1.38-42.\x* umHori\x + \xt 14.6. Dute. 2.12,22.\x*, abahlali belizwe: ULotani loShobhali loZibeyoni loAna
\v 21 loDishoni loEzeri loDishani; laba bayizinduna zamaHori, amadodana kaSeyiri elizweni leEdoma.
\v 22 Amadodana-ke kaLotani ayengoHori loHemama; lodadewabo kaLotani wayenguTimina\x + \xt 36.12.\x*.
\v 23 Lalaba ngamadodana kaShobhali: UAlivani loManahathi loEbhali, uShefo loOnama.
\v 24 Lalaba ngamadodana kaZibeyoni: Bobabili uAya loAna; unguAna owafica imithombo etshisayo enkangala eselusa obabhemi bakaZibeyoni uyise.
\v 25 Lalaba ngamadodana kaAna: UDishoni; loAholibama wayeyindodakazi kaAna\x + \xt 36.2.\x*.
\v 26 Lalaba ngamadodana kaDishoni: UHemidani loEshibhani loJitrani loKerani.
\v 27 Laba ngamadodana kaEzeri: UBilihani loZahavana loAkani.
\v 28 Laba ngamadodana kaDishani: UUzi loArani.
\v 29 Lezi zinduna zamaHori\x + \xt 36.20.\x*: Induna uLotani, induna uShobhali, induna uZibeyoni, induna uAna,
\v 30 induna uDishoni, induna uEzeri, induna uDishani; lezi zinduna zamaHori, ngezinduna zabo elizweni leSeyiri.
\s Amakhosi elizwe lakoEdoma
\p
\v 31 Lala ngamakhosi abusa elizweni leEdoma, inkosi ingakabusi abantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + \xt 1 Lan. 1.43-54.\x*.
\v 32 UBhela indodana kaBeyori wasebusa eEdoma, lebizo lomuzi wakhe laliyiDinihaba.
\v 33 UBhela wasesifa, uJobabi indodana kaZera weBozira wasebusa esikhundleni sakhe.
\v 34 UJobabi wasesifa, uHushama-ke owelizweni lamaTemani wabusa esikhundleni sakhe.
\v 35 UHushama wasesifa, uHadadi-ke indodana kaBedadi, owatshaya uMidiyani egcekeni lakoMowabi, wabusa esikhundleni sakhe; lebizo lomuzi wakhe laliyiAvithi.
\v 36 UHadadi wasesifa, uSamila-ke weMasireka wabusa esikhundleni sakhe.
\v 37 USamila wasesifa, uShawuli-ke weRehobothi\x + \xt Gen. 10.11.\x* emfuleni wabusa esikhundleni sakhe.
\v 38 UShawuli wasesifa, uBhali-Hanani-ke\x + \xt 1 Lan. 1.50.\x* indodana kaAkhibhori wabusa esikhundleni sakhe.
\v 39 UBhali-Hanani indodana kaAkhibhori wasesifa, uHadari-ke wabusa esikhundleni sakhe; lebizo lomuzi wakhe laliyiPawu; lebizo lomkakhe lalinguMehethabheli, indodakazi kaMatiredi, indodakazi kaMezahabhi.
\p
\v 40 Njalo la ngamabizo ezinduna zakoEsawu ngezizukulwana zazo, ngendawo zazo, ngamabizo azo\x + \xt 1 Lan. 1.51.\x*: Induna uTimina, induna uAliva, induna uJethethi,
\v 41 induna uAholibama, induna uEla, induna uPinoni,
\v 42 induna uKenazi, induna uTemani, induna uMibhizari,
\v 43 induna uMagidiyeli, induna uIrama; lezi zinduna zeEdoma, ngokwakha kwabo, elizweni lemfuyo yabo; lo nguEsawu, uyise kaEdoma.
